DESIGN AUTOMATION IS CHANGING MORE RAPIDLY TODAY THAN EVER BEFORE, EVEN FIVE YEARS AGO ITS GROWTH RATE WAS COMPARATIVELY SLOW, AND INTEREST IN THE FIELD WAS CONFINED PRIMARILY TO A FEW ORGANIZATIONS, TODAY, SPURRED ON BY GOVERNMENT INFUSION OF RESOURCES FOR THE VHISIC PROGRAM, INTEREST IN DESIGN AUTOMATION HAS DEVELOPED NEW INTENSITY, INDEED, THE DEFENSE DEPARTMENT CHOSE SIX ORGANIZATIONS FOR PHASE ZERO OF VHISIC,